FBIS3-18078 "drweu039aa_94011" FBIS-WEU-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 February 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Western Leaders Comment on Hebron Mosque Massacre Austria's Klestil Expresses `Dismay' AU2602202594 Vienna ORF Television Network in German 1830 GMT 26 Feb 94 AU2602202594 Vienna ORF Television Network Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] President Thomas Klestil sent a telegram of condolence to PLO leader Yasir 'Arafat. He expressed consternation and dismay over the mass murder. The Hebron massacre has demonstrated clearer than ever before that the peace process in the Middle East is indispensable, the president wrote.
